data.description: Welcome to your new home, perfectly situated on an oversized cul-de-sac lot. This beautiful home offers five spacious bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms. With its open layout and abundant natural light, the home feels airy and welcoming. The well-appointed kitchen is generously sized and features granite countertops and ample cabinet space for all your storage needs. The primary bedroom is conveniently located on the first floor and offers a soaking tub, a separate standing shower, and a large walk-in closet with plenty of storage capabilities. Upstairs, you'll find the additional bedrooms along with a versatile family/game room, providing plenty of space for relaxation and entertainment. The backyard has an abundance of space and offers privacy with no back neighbors, providing a peaceful retreat. A lovely two-car garage coupled with convenient access to freeways, shopping and dining will make this a house you want to call home. Don't wait, schedule your showing today!
